message.body: Lindsey!! What time should we do massage tomorrow?? Should we just hang and drink wine after or should we go to cantina??
Hey! I have yoga at 6-7:30. Tryin not to miss it cause I missed 3 in a row! We could do massage and hang time after at 8 or try Friday if you wanna go to the cantina!
I wanna go to the cantina!
I'm also free in the day tmw
Ok cool! Maybe we can try and do massage tomorrow afternoon and then go to cantina after you get out of yoga??
Yes that's perfect if it works for you! P
Cool! I'm not sure what time in the afternoon works, but I'll let you know in the morning if that's cool!
Can't wait for some qt at cantina!!
Yeah no prob! God I really want a fajita!
Tess! I'm not gonna do yoga tonight cause I worked out this morning. So we can do a later massage if you wanna.
Cool! Do you wanna do massage and then go to dinner or do you need a break after massage before we go to cantina??
Maybe like a half hour or hour to clean up and look like normal! Ha. But not too long
Ok so maybe massage at 4:30 and leave for cantina around 6:30?
